{"tid":1375237,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 科技樹 ] 傾斜裝甲 + 間隙式裝甲 討論","createTime":"2019-07-28T04:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T06:31:00.000Z","uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a667fa0a6870b9c369750f4806dc9b5411f8935","tid":1375237,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/装甲#傾斜裝甲\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%A3%85%E7%94%B2%23%E5%82%BE%E6%96%9C%E8%A3%9D%E7%94%B2&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp16E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=b6cc8c94\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/装甲#傾斜裝甲</a><br />\n以傾斜方式部署的裝甲可以利用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">斜面反彈砲彈</span></strong>，就算砲彈穿入也能有較長對角線阻擋砲彈，目前所有裝甲部署方式都是傾斜式。 <br />\n<br />\n傾斜裝甲可以將粒彈既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">平移動能轉化為旋轉動能, 大大減低穿透力</span></strong><br />\n角度越大, 理論上平移動能會越少<br />\n下面有片睇完就明<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/装甲#間隙式裝甲\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%A3%85%E7%94%B2%23%E9%96%93%E9%9A%99%E5%BC%8F%E8%A3%9D%E7%94%B2&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp16E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=1dc2a1fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/装甲#間隙式裝甲</a><br />\n惠普爾防護罩即使用間隙式裝甲的原理來保護穿梭機承受高速微流星體的撞擊。當第一層防護罩被撞擊時會打散或破壞襲來的衝擊物，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">促使碎片在之後的隔層內散佈較大的範圍，以分散撞擊內層防護罩時的能量。 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n不過小心<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果太斜真係彈左彈 彈撚左落個口度就仆街</span></strong> <br />\n所以最好第一層係預佢穿透 可以trap住粒彈<br />\n<br />\n示意動畫<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sYZNwbdntsU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsYZNwbdntsU&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp16E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=601b7e26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sYZNwbdntsU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/manutantraders/image/upload/t_400-scale/v15/ironmongery/products/145100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.cloudinary.com%2Fmanutantraders%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Ft_400-scale%2Fv15%2Fironmongery%2Fproducts%2F145100.jpg&h=ffb8fdf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d020616532d68e0ca53cb2e50991a9d5d23f2d42","tid":1375237,"uid":68822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:14:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp16E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=5ce254a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n\t</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n勿忘初衷，五大訴求！</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7.28  中上環 下午3點 遮打花園<br />\n捍衛自由 不徹不散<br />\n五大訴求</span></strong></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選"},{"pid":"7c6190f100210c138cd2b1343c867a99bf39bcc0","tid":1375237,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"轉過去學術台多啲人睇"},{"pid":"1d5c2e18938988b34edfa2d132b69c6ee1eaf730","tid":1375237,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c6190f100210c138cd2b1343c867a99bf39bcc0","tid":1375237,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"轉過去學術台多啲人睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:16:54.000Z","msg":"仆街開錯台...."},{"pid":"f3f64aad06e855c4152f999c93e7a5d3f1408f5f","tid":1375237,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"中間要放海綿等物料吸收衝力？"},{"pid":"80ad95c7